      <title>迪拜房地产热潮让买家想方设法抢占地盘</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-23/dubai-real-estate-boom-investors-eying-reits-fractional-ownership-apps</link>
      <description><![CDATA[迪拜已逐渐成为全球最热门的房地产市场之一，但其房价却越来越高，买家也因此对房地产投资信托的兴趣再度燃起，许多人开始转向分期付款仅需 136 美元的房地产部分所有权应用程序。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-23/dubai-real-estate-boom-investors-eying-reits-fractional-ownership-apps</guid>
      <pubDate>Sat, 23 Nov 2024 13:29:50 GMT</pubDate>
